<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4239868464532958783">Edmond Cheng, is of Chinese descent, from Hong Kong. He is a fan of suspense and it has always been his dream to produce a story with a unique theme. In 2011, he finished his debut novel, Illusion. He finds himself interested in things intriguing like time traveling and fingerprint analysis. Discussions on whether it is feasible for humans to build a UFO interests him. As a person with intense cur</span>
  <span id="freeText4239868464532958783" style="display:none">Edmond Cheng, is of Chinese descent, from Hong Kong. He is a fan of suspense and it has always been his dream to produce a story with a unique theme. In 2011, he finished his debut novel, Illusion. He finds himself interested in things intriguing like time traveling and fingerprint analysis. Discussions on whether it is feasible for humans to build a UFO interests him. As a person with intense curiosity, he almost had a DNA test done upon hearing his maternal great grandfather is Caucasian. Now he has finally found his destiny as a writer to share his stories with his readers. </span>
  <a data-text-id="4239868464532958783" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

